   Hou, Qin-zheng; Pang, Xia; Sun, Kun; Jia, Ling-yun; Zhang, Shi-hu; Li, Qiao-xia, Northwest Normal Univ, Coll Life Sci, Lanzhou 730030, Gansu, Peoples R China.
