   Jabbour, Florian; Damerval, Catherine, Univ Paris 11, CNRS, INRA, UMR Genet Vegetale, F-91190 Gif Sur Yvette, France.
   De Craene, Louis P. Ronse, Royal Bot Garden Edinburgh, Edinburgh EH3 5LR, Midlothian, Scotland.},
