   Hou, Qinzheng; Zhao, Xiang; Pang, Xia; Duan, Meiling; Ehmet, Nurbiye; Shao, Wenjuan; Sun, Kun, Northwest Normal Univ, Coll Life Sci, Lanzhou 730070, Gansu, Peoples R China.},
